'''保罗·霍夫曼'''（{{lang-en|Paul Hoffman}}，{{bd|1956年|3月30日|}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[大众科学|科普]]作家<ref name="mediabistro">{{cite web |url=http://www.mediabistro.com/articles/details.asp?aID=9816& |title=SO WHAT DO YOU DO, PAUL HOFFMAN, AUTHOR, ASME-WINNING WRITER |publisher=Mediabistro |date=August 22, 2007 |accessdate=January 4, 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906175516/http://www.mediabistro.com/articles/details.asp?aID=9816& |dead-url=no }}</ref>，现居于[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[泽西市|泽西市]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Paul Hoffman Named President and CEO|url=http://ceo.lsc.org/|work=Liberty Science Center Web site|publisher=Liberty Science Center|accessdate=2011-10-19|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008195253/http://ceo.lsc.org/|archivedate=2011-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要作品有《数字情种：[[埃尔德什·帕尔|埃尔德什]]传》（''The Man Who Loved Only Numbers: The Story of Paul Erdos and the Search for Mathematical Truth''）等。

